modShortDescription: This mod enabled certain blocks to be picked up after being placed. Modified blocks are: Wood Spikes and Iron Spikes.
modDescription:
This mod enabled certain blocks to be picked up after being placed.

Modified blocks are:

* Wood [Spikes](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-spikes/)
* Iron Spikes
